pokedexEntries.gold: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it suddenly extends the claws and startles its enemy.
pokedexEntries.silver: Vicious in nature, it drives Pidgey from their nests and feasts on the eggs that are left behind.
pokedexEntries.crystal: This cunning Pokémon hides in the cover of darkness, waiting to attack its prey.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into bark. It seeks out unguarded nests and steals Eggs for food while its parents are away.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into bark. It seeks out unguarded nests and steals Eggs for food while its parents are away.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into bark. It seeks out unguarded nests and steals Eggs for food while its parents are away.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: Vicious in nature, it drives Pidgey from their nests and feasts on the Eggs that are left behind.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it suddenly extends the claws and startles its enemy.
pokedexEntries.diamond: It feeds on Eggs stolen from nests. Its sharply hooked claws rip vulnerable spots on prey.
pokedexEntries.pearl: It is extremely vicious and will not stop attacking until its foe is incapable of moving.
pokedexEntries.platinum: A smart and sneaky Pokémon. A pair may work together to steal Eggs by having one lure the parents away.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it suddenly extends the claws and startles its enemy.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Vicious in nature, it drives Pidgey from their nests and scavenges any leftovers it can find.
pokedexEntries.black: A smart and sneaky Pokémon. A pair may work together to steal Eggs by having one lure the parents away.
pokedexEntries.white: A smart and sneaky Pokémon. A pair may work together to steal Eggs by having one lure the parents away.
pokedexEntries.black2: A smart and sneaky Pokémon, it makes its opponents flinch by suddenly showing the claws hidden in its paws.
pokedexEntries.white2: A smart and sneaky Pokémon, it makes its opponents flinch by suddenly showing the claws hidden in its paws.
pokedexEntries.x: It feeds on eggs stolen from nests. Its sharply hooked claws rip vulnerable spots on prey.
pokedexEntries.y: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it suddenly extends the claws and startles its enemy.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into bark. It seeks out unguarded nests and steals Eggs for food while its parents are away.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into bark. It seeks out unguarded nests and steals Eggs for food while its parents are away.
pokedexEntries.sun: It has a cunning yet savage disposition. It waits for parents to leave their nests, and then it sneaks in to steal their eggs.
pokedexEntries.moon: It uses its claws to poke holes in eggs so it can slurp out the insides. Breeders consider it a scourge and will drive it away or eradicate it.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: They will cooperate to steal eggs from the nests of bird Pokémon, but fights break out to determine which one gets to eat the eggs.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: It blends into the dark of night to ambush its prey. Sneasel will attack Sandshrew, but its hard skin can cause Sneasel’s claws to snap off.
